<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" href="login.css" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Jua&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>Document</title>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar">
            <div class="nav_logo">
                <a href="main.html"><img class="cocktail-logo" src="logo.svg"></a>
            </div>

            <ul class="nav_menu">
                <li><a href="main.html">오늘의 칵테일 검색하기</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">마이 페이지</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">전체 리스트</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">맞춤 칵테일</a></li>
                <li><a class='login' href="login.html">로그인</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class='user'>
        <div class='lg_title'>
            로그인
        </div>
        <div class='lg_elements'>
<%= form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: session_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
  <div class="field userid">
    <%= f.label :Email %>
    
    <%= f.email_field :email, autofocus: true, autocomplete: "email", :class => "inputbox_id" %>
    
</div>

  <div class="field password">
    
    <%= f.label :비밀번호 %>
    
    <%= f.password_field :password, autocomplete: "current-password", :class => "inputbox_pw" %>
  </div>

  <div class="actions lg_btn">
        <%= f.submit "로그인", :class => "button" %>
  </div>

<% end %>


            <div class='signup'>
                <a href = "/users/sign_up">회원가입 하러가기</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <div class="creators">만든 이들: 고민정, 김시연, 김채린, 서예빈, 홍노아</div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>


